Name: Forklift & Box
About the game: welcome player, this is my first game that I've Made. The objective is to take the lift and move boxes around the maze tell you get to the stripped areas . You push the red boxes in the striped zones for points and to be able to go to the next level. There are four different levels and the objective is to get the most points. so good luck and have fun.
